{"tid":936144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好老實講句，再冇人抖中國，遲早全世界都係中國既","createTime":"2018-12-10T13:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T15:02:27.000Z","uid":141072,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5f92db2fa158de361c37023a6e787f8ab185d1","tid":936144,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"非洲失守左好耐<br />\n歐盟做啞狗，自己堆債務同國事都有排搞<br />\n美國虎頭蛇尾，貿易戰勝算又越黎越細<br />\n日本又淨係睇美國頭<br />\n台灣、香港既人都係想安於現況多過想搞抗爭<br />\n澳洲更加唔使講，出既入既貨都係中國<br />\n<br />\n再唔趁依家中國未有防備既時候殺個措手不及，係中國自己玩完之前肯定已經坐大全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講句，香港係2047之前就會完成裝設唔知幾萬個天眼，點解個社會都係好似冇人識驚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d廢老短視啫，點解成個世界咁唔合理都會可以一日再衰過一日<br />\n<br />\n2019 WWIII，事在必行<br />\n我就唔信有人會講到冇WWIII而有另一個美好未來既可能性"},{"pid":"80b98c91bf3854034e2c25f45471a4b94121308e","tid":936144,"uid":12754,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"你係咪諗多左"},{"pid":"193fb22cd7f32d01bd6ea4004ea63dc245175f41","tid":936144,"uid":43428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"呢個笑話睇得出你好有心思<br />\n我比十分"},{"pid":"882745dc40ee61fea34db860ce2aa6b186a69ddb","tid":936144,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"美國虎頭蛇尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講咁多,唧係支那又羸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39584bab6e918f239e3cb96dc7f10b2d1746936b","tid":936144,"uid":219281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ff4af8b0652cb4f859e7669a1bc78624793b54","tid":936144,"uid":141